      • calculateSYMBOLICimportance

        @Deprecated
public void calculateSYMBOLICimportance(ClusNode node,
                                                     double[] weights,
                                                     double depth)
                                              throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Deprecated. 
        Recursively computes the symbolic importance of attributes, importance(attribute) = importance(attribute, node), where

        importance(attribute, node) = (0.0 : 1.0 ? node has attribute as a test) + sum_subnodes weight * importance(attribute, subnode),

        for all weights in weights.

        Parameters:
        depth - Depth of node, root's depth is 0
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException
